This module is a rollup of the following modules:

  • controls
  • core
    Fundamental abstractions in the architecture.
  • facets
    Common abstractions for computing shader uniform variables.
  • geometries
    A convenience class for creating an arrow.
  • materials
    Utilities for the construction of WebGLShader code.
  • math
    Geometric Algebra and Mathematical abstractions.
  • visual
    Convenient abstractions for Physics modeling.
